Love is sitting in the middle of a bench,
when there is plenty of room at both ends
Remembered, never forgotten
March 2020"╗
ĖIn Loving Memory of Simon Peter Read
Born 29th June 1971, died 12th July 1997 aged 26.
So young, so much to live for, so brave.
Forever in our thoughts, Mum, Dad and all the family."╩
ŪRemembering Harold F Jopson 1925-2010
who loved to walk here
"Peace be with you" John 20 v.19

In loving memory of
Jean Margaret Jopson (1933-2012)
To whom friends and family were most precious"ß
▐In loving memory of Albert Victor Gray 1915 - 2000
a New Forest visitor who loved to sit here,
watching and dreaming, we hope you do too.
Also, in loving memory of his beloved wife
Cecily Lysbeth Grace Gray 1915 - 2008"Ń
